flowchart TB
    U[用户浏览器] --> FE[LifePilot 前端]
    FE --> BE[LifePilotServer 5000]
    BE --> MCP[LifePilot_mcp 7000]
    BE --> RAG[ai-server 7100]

    MCP --> MYSQL[(MySQL 任务与用户数据)]
    BE --> MONGO[(MongoDB 对话记录)]
    BE --> REDIS[(Redis 调度队列)]

    RAG --> WEAV[(Weaviate 向量检索)]
    RAG --> QDR[(Qdrant 检索索引)]
    RAG --> NEO[(Neo4j 图结构)]
    RAG --> OSS[(七牛对象存储)]

    FE --> LOG[Metaphorical 日志服务]
    LOG --> LOGDB[(MongoDB 日志库)]